fields.title: Easy Veggie Stir Fry
fields.description: A quick and healthy vegetable stir fry recipe.
fields.ingredients: Carrot, Broccoli, Bell pepper, Soy sauce, Garlic, Olive oil
fields.instructions: 1. Chop vegetables. 2. Stir fry in olive oil. 3. Add soy sauce and garlic. 4. Serve hot.

fields.title: Chicken Caesar Salad
fields.description: A fresh, healthy chicken salad with Caesar dressing.
fields.ingredients: Chicken breast, Romaine lettuce, Caesar dressing, Parmesan, Croutons, Lemon
fields.instructions: 1. Grill the chicken breast. 2. Toss lettuce, croutons, and dressing. 3. Add sliced chicken and top with Parmesan.

fields.title: Vegetarian Tacos
fields.description: Tacos filled with roasted vegetables and a delicious salsa.
fields.ingredients: Corn tortillas, Bell peppers, Zucchini, Onion, Garlic, Black beans, Salsa, Avocado, Cilantro
fields.instructions: 1. Roast the vegetables. 2. Warm the tortillas. 3. Fill with roasted veggies, black beans, salsa, and avocado.
